Today was most definately toataly kick ass, I wok up at 10 ready to kick ass at paintball, and whataya know, I did. I won both games of woodsball, and ofcourse all my games of speedball. It is so sad, cuz I had pat on my team for woodsball, and he is the worst fucking defender ever, he took th hostage, and walked her down the road twards where she was suposed to be rescued by the other team at and got lit up, so i alone had to take the other 2 out before they could get the hostage out of there. I even took 3 on 1 and destroyed them, Pat attempted the same feat and ended up getting raped by me and my blood paint. I hapen to have video to prove all of this.

Whats also great about today is Stephanie<3 got back from LA today, and I got to talk to her, i was so happy. I also gt to go to the beach with her tomorow :). But i'm tired so I'm going to go to sleep. so see you all later.

Thats right today I fell asleep at 2 (I mised BSG at 10 cuz i was kicken ass at halo at Chris M's house with Romero, Nials, Chris M., and Alex till 11), that was fun, we had a convoy of cars at my house (2 cars) and I got to ride in alex's truck, thank god he's such a beter driver than pat, when we got to romero's house we set up 3 T.V's and 3 x-boxes for 5 ppl, it ended up bein -AE-(me and alex) vs the others (Chris, Romero, and Nials). I didn't get dinner that night, but luckaly we had pizza mmmmmmmmm. 

Boy howdy was I tired too, i only got 4 hours of sleep the night B4. And then when I wake up I find that my internet is out NOOOOOO, but as you can see now it's fixed :). Oh by the way I got ur mesages back Steph, it's always good to hear from you when your gone <3. 

This brings me to my third paragraph, where I tell you that I play paintball tomorow :). The people playing are Me, Alex, Romero, Pat, and Rae. Romero just got a Spider rodeo so that gives us enough guns for the confirmed 5 of us. Alex is planning on getting a gun so we don't have to use are extrs that much, but for the newbies (like steph and rae) who will prolly be playing with us quite a bit, we will now have extras for you guys. It'd be cool if you got a gun too tho Steph, then we could have more ppl to play even more often. Which would be awsome. It also gets me closer to the dream of having my own sponserd paintball team.

Well i'm thinking about playing some online games or doing something other than just sit here and type about my day and such, but i don't think you all realy care that much, atualy I don't realy thing anyone will read this, I almost know nobody will read this far, so I'm just gona go play Counter strike or something so I'll see you all tomrow, and for Steph I'll see you when you get back <3.

<3 Love always <3
-Connor
